                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2606.28276/2606.28276v1/figs/imgs/cousins/coffee_2/frame_0001.jpg",
                "caption": "Figure 3:SimFoundry Scene Generation Samples.We show real-world input images (top row), the corresponding reconstructed digital twins generated by SimFoundry (middle), and sampled digital cousin scene variations (bottom). For instance, in the scene that is second from the left, the brown glass bottle becomes narrower for the cousin scene, and in the scene that is third from the right, the digital cousin of the wicker basket has holes near the top that can plausibly be used as handles, while the layout of the scene also changes.",
